Metro Likely to Decide on Cordes’s Future This Month, FTD Says

-- B y   C o r n e l i u s   R a h n
-- 
2011-09-13T05:37:20Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-13/metro-likely-to-decide-on-cordes-s-future-this-month-ftd-says.html
Metro AG (MEO)  will probably decide by
the end of the month whether to replace Chief Executive Officer
Eckard Cordes, the  Financial Times Deutschland  reported, citing
people on the company’s supervisory board.  Cordes is facing “extensive” opposition in the board, the
newspaper said, adding that some members are still undecided.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Cornelius Rahn in Frankfurt at 
 crahn2@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Kenneth Wong in Berlin at 
 kwong11@bloomberg.net  